&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time and a cell phone number including country code in the &ldquo;Special Requests&rdquo; area of the booking form&lt;/li&gt;
